ievement, 2 (two) copies of passport size photograph and copies of other relevant papers addressing the Executive Director, Village Education Resource Center, B-30, Ekhlas Uddin Khan Road, Anandapur, Savar, Dhaka-1340</p>\r\n\r\n<p>আবেদনকারীকে অবশ্যই জীবনবৃত্তান্তের সাথে&nbsp;ছবি&nbsp;পাঠাতে হবে</p>\r\n\r\n<p>আবেদনের শেষ তারিখ :&nbsp;<strong>জুলাই ২৭, ২০১৭</strong></p>\r\n', '2017-07-13 21:14:04', '2017-07-13 21:14:04', 1, 'Mamun Shahriar', '1', 'bangla', '', 0, 0),
(1500002108, 4, 'Online Marketing Executive', 'featured_images_1500002108.jpeg', '', '', '<h2>Develop IT Limited</h2>\r\n\r\n<p><a href="javascript:void(0)" onclick="ga(''send'', ''event'', ''/bn/jobdetailsBN.asp'', ''click'', ''View all jobs of this company from Top'', 1);">এই কোম্পানির অন্যান্য সব চাকরি</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>চাকরির মূল তথ্য</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Applicant must have good Skill on Computer &amp; Internet Operating.</li>\r\n	<li>This job is available for Day &amp; night Shift.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>খালি পদের সংখ্যা</p>\r\n\r\n<p>৫০</p>\r\n\r\n<p>চাকরির বিবরণ / দায়িত্বসমূহ</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Create content for social media marketing campaigns</li>\r\n	<li>Write engaging and persuasive content for a variety of channels</li>\r\n	<li>Measure and report on the effectiveness of content marketing and social media programs and campaigns</li>\r\n	<li>Identify trends and insights, and optimize spend and performance based on the insight</li>\r\n	<li>Brainstorm new and creative growth strategies</li>\r\n	<li>Plan, execute, and measure experiments and conversion tests</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>চাকরির ধরন</p>\r\n\r\n<p>ফুল টাইম</p>\r\n\r\n<p>শিক্ষাগত যোগ্যতা</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>HSC/ Diploma</li>\r\n	<li>Freshers are welcome.</li>\r\n	<li>Education Qualifications are no barrier for the skilled person.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>অন্যান্য যোগ্যতা</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>বয়স ১৮ থেকে ২৫ বছর</li>\r\n	<li>শুধুমাত্র পুরুষরা আবেদন করতে পারবেন</li>\r\n	<li>Excellent writing, reading and editing skills (English)</li>\r\n	<li>Manage multiple priorities and projects</li>\r\n	<li>Familiarity with search engines and social media channels</li>\r\n	<li>Internet marketing</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>কর্মস্হল</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Dhaka (Tejgaon, Uttara)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>বেতন সীমা</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>টাকা. ৬০০০ - ৮০০০</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>অন্যান্য&nbsp;সুবিধাদি</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Others Benefits are available according to Company policy.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>উত্স</p>\r\n\r\n<p