(1500002195, 4, 'Game Developer', 'featured_images_1500002195.jpeg', '', '', '<p>খালি পদের সংখ্যা<br />\r\n০১<br />\r\nচাকরির প্রাসঙ্গিক বর্ণনা<br />\r\nUnity3D, Construct 2,BuildBox,Coocos2d-JS<br />\r\nProgramming C#, Unity Script<br />\r\nMicrosoft Office<br />\r\nচাকরির বিবরণ / দায়িত্বসমূহ<br />\r\nDeveloping 2D/3D Android games using Unity3D<br />\r\nDeveloping HTML5,Android Games with any 2D Game Engine(i.e. Construct 2,BuildBox, Coocos2d-JS)<br />\r\nUpdating Existing Games Developed in Unity.<br />\r\nDevelop and maintain the test approach for your designated areas of the product<br />\r\nShould be able to multi-task, work with a sense of urgency and adapt to changing requirement and project directions<br />\r\nচাকরির ধরন<br />\r\nফুল টাইম<br />\r\nশিক্ষাগত যোগ্যতা<br />\r\nB.Sc. in Computer Science from any reputed University.<br />\r\nঅভিজ্ঞতা<br />\r\n১ থেকে ২ বছর<br />\r\nচাকরিপ্রার্থীদের যেসব ক্ষেত্রে অভিজ্ঞতা থাকতে হবেঃ<br />\r\nProgrammer/Software Engineer, Mobile apps developer<br />\r\nচাকরিপ্রার্থীদের যেসব ব্যবসায়িক প্রতিষ্ঠানে অভিজ্ঞতা থাকতে হবেঃ<br />\r\nIT Enabled Service, Software Company<br />\r\nঅন্যান্য যোগ্যতা<br />\r\nবয়স ১৮ থেকে ৩৫ বছর<br />\r\nGame Development Experience in Unity3D or any 2D Game Engine<br />\r\nProper Knowledge in C# or Unity Script in (Monodevelop) Unity<br />\r\nStrong analytical skill<br />\r\nExceptionally self-motivated and directed<br />\r\nDebugging, problem-solving skills and object-oriented approach<br />\r\nকর্মস্হল<br />\r\nDhaka Division<br />\r\nবেতন সীমা<br />\r\nআলোচনা সাপেক্ষ<br />\r\nঅন্যান্য&nbsp;সুবিধাদি<br />\r\nAs per company rules.<br />\r\nউত্স<br />\r\nBdjobs.com Online Job Posting</p>\r\n', '2017-07-13 21:16:35', '2017-07-13 21:16:35', 1, 'Mamun Shahriar', '1', 'bangla', '', 0, 0),
(1500002268, 4, 'Brothers Fashion Limited (A Concern of TEAM Group)  Brothers Fashion Limited (A Concern of TEAM Group)', 'featured_images_1500002268.jpeg', '', '', '<p>Job Description / Responsibility</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Handling Customer individually starting from order taking, sample development to shipment</li>\r\n	<li>Preparing Garments costing</li>\r\n	<li>Monitoring production and resolving all order related issues</li>\r\n	<li>Coordinating and following up with QC department, commercial department, accessories factory etc. and other relevant entity to ensure smooth production, shipment and payment</li>\r\n	<li>Communicating with customer regularly</li>\r\n	<li>Following up with Merchandiser - QA meeting</li>\r\n	<li>Checking WIP, master file and central portal update</li>\r\n	<li>Managing all issues to ensure timely shipment with quality product</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Job Nature</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Full-time</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Educational Requirements</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>B. Sc in Textile Engineering/ Apparel Manufacturing/ MBA in Merchandising or Master in any discipline from any recognized university.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Experience Requirements</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>At least 3 year(s)</li>\r\n	<li>The applicants should have experience in the following area(s):<br />\r\n	Merchandising</li>\r\n	<li>The applicants should have experience in the following business area(s):<br />\r\n	Group of Companies, Garments</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Job Requirements</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Only males are allowed to apply.</li>\r\n	<li>Strong communication in English.</li>\r\n	<li>Must have sound knowledge in Woven (Denim/ Non Denim).</li>\r\n	<li>Possess high degree of correspondence.</li>\r\n	<li>Computer knowledge in E-mail, Internet, Word and Excel is a must with the need to produce reports for management and clients.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Job Location</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Gazipur</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Salary Range</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Negotiable</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Other Benefits</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>As per the company policy.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Job Source</p>\r\n', '2017-07-13 21:17:48', '2017-07-13 23:34:15', 1, 'Mamun Shahriar', '1', 'bangla', '', 0, 0),
(1500002325, 4, 'এক্সিকিউটিভ (লোকাল পারচেস)', 'featured_images_1500002326.jpeg', '', '', '<p>এক্সিকিউটিভ (লোকাল পারচেস)</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>হরিজন প্লাস্টিক ইন্ডাস্ট্রিজ লিঃ</h2>\r\n\r\n<p><a href="javascript:void(0)" onclick="ga(''send'', ''event'', ''/bn/jobdetailsBN.asp'', ''click'', ''View all jobs of this company from Top'', 1);">এই কোম্পানির অন্যান্য সব চাকরি</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>খালি পদের সংখ্যা</p>\r\n\r\n<p>০১</p>\r\n\r\n<p>চাকরির প্রাসঙ্গিক বর্ণনা</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>মেটেরিয়াল, সাপ্লাই এর এবং অথবা সরঞ্জামের অর্ডার গ্রহণ এবং শিপমেন্ট এবং ডেলিভারীর ক্ষেত্রে ভেন্ডরদের ফলোআপ করা।</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>চাকরির বিবরণ / দায়িত্বসমূহ</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>পারচেস রিকুইজিশন সংগ্রহ করা এবং সেই অনুসারে RFQ তৈরী করা।</li>\r\n	<li>RFQ সংগ্রহ এবং তুলনামূলক স্টেটমেন্ট তৈরী করা।</li>\r\n	<li>মেশিন এবং যন্ত্রাংশের সম্পর্কে টেকনিক্যাল জ্ঞান অর্জন করা ও সোর্সিং করা।</li>\r\n	<li>ভেন্ডর নির্বাচন এবং প্রয়োজন অনুসারে তাদের মূল্যায়ন করা।</li>\r\n	<li>পারচেস অর্ডার তৈরী এবং সঠিক সময়ে প্রয়োজন অনুসারে তা ফলোআপ দেওয়া।</li>\r\n	<li>লোকাল অথবা ক্যাশ পারচেস করা।</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>চাকরির ধরন</p>\r\n\r\n<p>ফুল টাইম</p>\r\n\r\n<p>শিক্ষাগত যোগ্যতা</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>যে কোন বিষয়ে মাস্টার্স</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>অভিজ্ঞতা</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>১ থেকে ৪ বছর</li>\r\n	<li>চাকরিপ্রার্থীদের যেসব ক্ষেত্রে অভিজ্ঞতা থাকতে হবেঃ<br />\r\n	Commercial, Purchase/Procurement, Supply Chain</li>\r\n	<li>চাকরিপ্রার্থীদের যেসব ব্যবসায়িক প্রতিষ্ঠানে অভিজ্ঞতা থাকতে হবেঃ<br />\r\n	পাইকারী, প্লাস্টিক / পলিমার শিল্প, প্যাকেজিং শিল্প</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>অন্যান্য যোগ্যতা</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>শুধুমাত্র পুরুষরা আবেদন করতে পারবেন</li>\r\n	<li>মাইক্রোসফট অফিস প্যাকেজে ভাল জ্ঞান।</li>\r\n	<li>ব্যাপক ভ্রমণের আগ্রহ।</li>\r\n	<li>প্রয়োজন অনুসারে কোম্পানী কর্তৃক অন্যত্র স্থানান্তর হতে আগ্রহ থাকতে হবে।</li>\r\n	<li>সংশ্লিষ্ট ক্ষেত্রে ২ থেকে ৩ বছরের অভিজ্ঞতা।</li>\r\n	<li>মাইক্রোসফট অফিস প্যাকেজে ভাল জ্ঞান।</li>\r\n	<li>ইআরপি এর জ্ঞান।</li>\r\n	<li>প্লাস্টিক প্যাকেজিং এর ক্ষেত্রে পরিচিতি থাকলে বাড়তি সুবিধা।</li>\r\n	<li>যন্ত্রাংশ সম্পর্কে জ্ঞান থাকলে বাড়তি সুবিধা।</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>কর্মস্হল</p>\r\n\r\n<p>বাংলাদেশের যেকোনো স্থানে</p>\r\n\r\n<p>বেতন সীমা</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>আলোচনা সাপেক্ষ</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '2017-07-13 21:18:46', '2017-07-13 21:18:46', 1, 'Mamun Shahriar', '1', 'bangla', '', 0, 0),
(1500002393, 4, 'Customer Care Specialist, Import', 'featured_images_1500002393.jpeg', '', '', '<p>Customer Care Specialist, Import</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Maersk Line</h2>\r\n\r\n<p><a href="javascript:void(0)" onclick="ga(''send'', ''event'', ''/bn/jobdetailsBN.asp'', ''click'', ''View all jobs of this company from Top'', 1);">এই কোম্পানির অন্যান্য সব চাকরি</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>খালি পদের সংখ্যা</p>\r\n\r\n<p>১</p>\r\n\r\n<p>চাকরির বিবরণ / দায়িত্বসমূহ</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Check for import cargo restrictions</li>\r\n	<li>Check all cargo to be discharged is manifested</li>\r\n	<li>Check shipments with open activities or missing updates</li>\r\n	<li>Check for mismatch next vessel/voyage discharge port</li>\r\n	<li>Check against CSOP for special requirements and country specific exceptions</li>\r\n	<li>Issue amendments to the manifest import.</li>\r\n	<li>Prepare supplementary manifest whenever required.</li>\r\n	<li>Check various BO &amp; marvel reports to find error and eliminate errors prior pull out manifest.</li>\r\n	<li>Send telex to load/transhipment port in-case of any error or missing information identified in GCSS based reports.</li>\r\n	<li>Communicate with GSC and ensure all BAN related B/Ls&#39; are manifested and ensure CSOP are properly followed and maintained by GSC with high standard of data quality.</li>\r\n	<li>Handle ROB/DIT as per global/enable</li>\r\n	<li>Build up excellent relationship with customers / relevant parties / authorities and ensure customers are served efficiently.</li>\r\n	<li>Ensure CSI score is always maintained as outstanding level.</li>\r\n	<li>Ensure to keep your pending tray neat and clean everyday and close all necessary tasks including &quot;Review notification &quot;task.</li>\r\n	<li>Ensure customers telephone calls are attended promptly and efficiently and give feedback professionally.</li>\r\n	<li>Telexes must be attended within 24 hours of receiving same to avoid reminders.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>চাকরির ধরন</p>\r\n\r\n<p>ফুল টাইম</p>\r\n\r\n<p>শিক্ষাগত যোগ্যতা</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Graduate from any reputable University</li>\r\n	<li>Should have minimum 2-3 years&#39; experience in shipping documentation, having In-depth knowledge of letter of credits, Bank negotiating instruments and process of negotiations, Local Banking and port, customs rules and restrictions regarding import.</li>\r\n	<li>Knowledge or customer service process and tools.</li>\r\n	<li>Experience in deriving the efficiencies from MGM.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>অভিজ্ঞতা</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>২ থেকে ৪ বছর</li>\r\n	<li>চাকরিপ্রার্থীদের যেসব ক্ষেত্রে অভিজ্ঞতা থাকতে হবেঃ<br />\r\n	Commercial, Export/Import through L/C, Documentation</li>\r\n	<li>চাকরিপ্রার্থীদের যেসব ব্যবসায়িক প্রতিষ্ঠানে অভিজ্ঞতা থাকতে হবেঃ<br />\r\n	Freight forwarding, Logistic/Courier/Air Express Companies, Shipping, Clearing &amp; Forwarding (C&amp;F) Companies</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>অন্যান্য যোগ্যতা</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Experience in working with various systems like GCSS, RKEM, GSIS, MARVEL, MEPC, BO (business object) etc.</li>\r\n	<li>Advanced knowledge on Microsoft office software.</li>\r\n	<li>Strive for functional excellence through functional knowledge.</li>\r\n	<li>Responsible for full interaction with other department / staff for optimal efficiency.</li>\r\n	<li>Plan, organise, guideline and run workshops.</li>\r\n	<li>Understand our clients, their business requirements and coordinate same so that we can provide best service to the customers.</li>\r\n	<li>Manage all aspects of the shipping process and share the knowledge among the team to focus on cost savings and deliver quality service to the customers.</li>\r\n	<li>Staff management and development</li>\r\n	<li>Risk management</li>\r\n	<li>Contingency management for critical processes</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>কর্মস্হল</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Chittagong</p>\r\n\r\n<p>উত্স</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Bdjobs.com Online Job Posting</p>\r\n\r\n<p>চাকরির সারসংক্ষেপ</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>প্রকাশ তারিখ:</strong>&nbsp;জুলাই ১৩, ২০১৭</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>খালি পদের সংখ্যা:</strong>&nbsp;১</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>চাকরির ধরন:</strong>&nbsp;ফুল টাইম</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>অভিজ্ঞতা:</strong>&nbsp;২ থেকে ৪ বছর</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>কর্মস্হল:</strong>&nbsp;Chittagong</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>আবেদনের শেষ তারিখ:</strong>&nbsp;জুলাই ২৭, ২০১৭</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href="javascript:void(0);" onclick="ga(''send'', ''event'', ''/bn/jobdetailsBN.asp'', ''click'', ''Shortlist this job'', 2);">&nbsp;শর্টলিস্ট</a><a href="javascript:void(0);" onclick="ga(''send'', ''event'', ''/bn/jobdetailsBN.asp'', ''click'', ''Share by Email'', 3);">&nbsp;ইমেইলে শেয়ার</a><a href="javascript:void(0);" onclick="printPage(714111);ga(''send'', ''event'', ''/bn/jobdetailsBN.asp'', ''click'', ''Print this job'', 4);">&nbsp;প্রিন্ট</a><a href="javascript:void(0);" onclick="ga(''send'', ''event'', ''/bn/jobdetailsBN.asp'', ''click'', '' View all jobs of this company'', 5);">&nbsp;এই কোম্পানির অন্যান্য সব চাকরি</a><a href="javascript:void(0);" onclick="ga(''send'', ''event'', ''/bn/jobdetailsBN.asp'', ''click'', ''Report this job'', 6);">&nbsp;রিপোর্ট</a></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>&nbsp;</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Courses from Bdjobs Training</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Pay online and get 20% discount</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href="http://bdjobstraining.com/trainingdetails.asp?TrainingId=91095&amp;upcoming=0">Export- Import Business Guideline with Commercial, Marketing, Costing &amp; Documentation Procedure</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Classes/ Sessions:</strong>&nbsp;2 Days Long</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Course Duration:</strong>&nbsp;21 - 22 July 2017</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href="http://bdjobstraining.com/trainingdetails.asp?TrainingId=91095&amp;upcoming=0" target="_blank">&nbsp;Click here for detail</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href="javascript:void(0);" onclick="javascript:document.getElementById(''frmJobApplication'').submit()">অনলাইনে আবেদন</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>অথবা</p>\r\n\r\n<p>আপনার জীবনবৃত্তান্ত যেখানে পাঠাবেন&nbsp;<strong>roshni.sanyal@maersk.com</strong>&nbsp;অথবা&nbsp;<strong>মাই বিডিজবসের</strong>&nbsp;মাধ্যমে পাঠাতে&nbsp;<a href="javascript:EmailSend()">এখানে ক্লিক করুন</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>আবেদনকারীকে অবশ্যই জীবনবৃত্তান্তের সাথে&nbsp;ছবি&nbsp;পাঠাতে হবে</p>\r\n\r\n<p>আবেদনের শেষ তারিখ :&nbsp;<strong>জুলাই ২৭, ২০১৭</strong></p>\r\n', '2017-07-13 21:19:53', '2017-07-13 21:19:53', 1, 'Mamun Shahriar', '1', 'bangla', '', 0, 0),
(1500002437, 4, 'Developer Wanted', 'featured_images_1500002437.jpeg', '', '', '<p>Customer Care Specialist, Import</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Maersk Line</h2>\r\n\r\n<p><a href="javascript:void(0)" onclick="ga(''send'', ''event'', ''/bn/jobdetailsBN.asp'', ''click'', ''View all jobs of this company from Top'', 1);">এই কোম্পানির অন্যান্য সব চাকরি</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>খালি পদের সংখ্যা</p>\r\n\r\n<p>১</p>\r\n\r\n<p>চাকরির বিবরণ / দায়িত্বসমূহ</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Job Description / Responsibility<br />\r\n	Acknowledgement of the order quantity in advance for making production plan and to liaise with the Management and to give necessary directives to the Production Manager of the unit regarding the production plan<br />\r\n	To give necessary directives to Production/Sample team to make a sample of a particular buyer in order to get the approval of mass production<br />\r\n	To keep close eyes in order to attain acceptable production limit and to ensure about the implementation of the production schedule. If any production manager fails to achieve the production target, then reason is to be found out from production manager and he is to be guided for more production<br />\r\n	Having clear idea about the quality of garments and to guide his subordinates to take necessary corrective measures if there is any problem of quality so that garments can be made exportable stage<br />\r\n	To implement price-controlled policy in every stage of production, so that production cost is reduced<br />\r\n	To make necessary arrangement of training for the subordinates in order to increase the production capability by following modern production procedure.<br />\r\n	To advise Production Manager to follow the production schedule<br />\r\n	To take the responsibility during an audit by the buyer regarding compliance issues<br />\r\n	To take all necessary safety measures in connection with the production<br />\r\n	To take necessary measures with the Admin, HR &amp; Compliance Dept. in order to uphold human rights and development of human resources</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '2017-07-13 21:20:37', '2017-07-13 23:31:28', 1, 'Mamun Shahriar', '1', 'bangla', '', 0, 0),
(1500002481, 4, 'Manager (Transport & Factory Goods Dispatch) SCM Factory  Meghna Group of Industries.', 'featured_images_1500002482.jpeg', '', '', '<p>Customer Care Specialist, Import</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href="javascript:void(0)" onclick="ga(''send'', ''event'', ''/bn/jobdetailsBN.asp'', ''click'', ''View all jobs of this company from Top'', 1);">এই কোম্পানির অন্যান্য সব চাকরি</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>খালি পদের সংখ্যা</p>\r\n\r\n<p>১</p>\r\n\r\n<p>চাকরির বিবরণ / দায়িত্বসমূহ</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Check for import cargo restrictions</li>\r\n	<li>Check all cargo to be discharged is manifested</li>\r\n	<li>Check shipments with open activities or missing updates</li>\r\n	<li>Check for mismatch next vessel/voyage discharge port</li>\r\n	<li>Check against CSOP for special requirements and country specific exceptions</li>\r\n	<li>Issue amendments to the manifest import.</li>\r\n	<li>Prepare supplementary manifest whenever required.</li>\r\n	<li>Check various BO &amp; marvel reports to find error and eliminate errors prior pull out manifest.</li>\r\n	<li>Send telex to load/transhipment port in-case of any error or missing information identified in GCSS based reports.</li>\r\n	<li>Communicate with GSC and ensure all BAN related B/Ls&#39; are manifested and ensure CSOP are properly followed and maintained by GSC with high standard of data quality.</li>\r\n	<li>Handle ROB/DIT as per global/enable</li>\r\n	<li>Build up excellent relationship with customers / relevant parties / authorities and ensure customers are served efficiently.</li>\r\n	<li>Ensure CSI score is always maintained as outstanding level.</li>\r\n	<li>Ensure to keep your pending tray neat and clean everyday and close all necessary tasks including &quot;Review notification &quot;task.</li>\r\n	<li>Ensure customers telephone calls are attended promptly and efficiently and give feedback professionally.</li>\r\n	<li>Telexes must be attended within 24 hours of receiving same to avoid reminders.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>চাকরির ধরন</p>\r\n\r\n<p>ফুল টাইম</p>\r\n\r\n<p>শিক্ষাগত যোগ্যতা</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Graduate from any reputable University</li>\r\n	<li>Should have minimum 2-3 years&#39; experience in shipping documentation, having In-depth knowledge of letter of credits, Bank negotiating instruments and process of negotiations, Local Banking and port, customs rules and restrictions regarding import.</li>\r\n	<li>Knowledge or customer service process and tools.</li>\r\n	<li>Experience in deriving the efficiencies from MGM.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>অভিজ্ঞতা</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>২ থেকে ৪ বছর</li>\r\n	<li>চাকরিপ্রার্থীদের যেসব ক্ষেত্রে অভিজ্ঞতা থাকতে হবেঃ<br />\r\n	Commercial, Export/Import through L/C, Documentation</li>\r\n	<li>চাকরিপ্রার্থীদের যেসব ব্যবসায়িক প্রতিষ্ঠানে অভিজ্ঞতা থাকতে হবেঃ<br />\r\n	Freight forwarding, Logistic/Courier/Air Express Companies, Shipping, Clearing &amp; Forwarding (C&amp;F) Companies</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>অন্যান্য যোগ্যতা</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Experience in working with various systems like GCSS, RKEM, GSIS, MARVEL, MEPC, BO (business object) etc.</li>\r\n	<li>Advanced knowledge on Microsoft office software.</li>\r\n	<li>Strive for functional excellence through functional knowledge.</li>\r\n	<li>Responsible for full interaction with other department / staff for optimal efficiency.</li>\r\n	<li>Plan, organise, guideline and run workshops.</li>\r\n	<li>Understand our clients, their business requirements and coordinate same so that we can provide best service to the customers.</li>\r\n	<li>Manage all aspects of the shipping process and share the knowledge among the team to focus on cost savings and deliver quality service to the customers.</li>\r\n	<li>Staff management and development</li>\r\n	<li>Risk management</li>\r\n	<li>Contingency management for critical processes</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>কর্মস্হল</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Chittagong</p>\r\n\r\n<p>উত্স</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Bdjobs.com Online Job Posting</p>\r\n\r\n<p>চাকরির সারসংক্ষেপ</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>প্রকাশ তারিখ:</strong>&nbsp;জুলাই ১৩, ২০১৭</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>খালি পদের সংখ্যা:</strong>&nbsp;১</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>চাকরির ধরন:</strong>&nbsp;ফুল টাইম</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>অভিজ্ঞতা:</strong>&nbsp;২ থেকে ৪ বছর</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>কর্মস্হল:</strong>&nbsp;Chittagong</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>আবেদনের শেষ তারিখ:</strong>&nbsp;জুলাই ২৭, ২০১৭</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href="javascript:void(0);" onclick="ga(''send'', ''event'', ''/bn/jobdetailsBN.asp'', ''click'', ''Shortlist this job'', 2);">&nbsp;শর্টলিস্ট</a><a href="javascript:void(0);" onclick="ga(''send'', ''event'', ''/bn/jobdetailsBN.asp'', ''click'', ''Share by Email'', 3);">&nbsp;ইমেইলে শেয়ার</a><a href="javascript:void(0);" onclick="printPage(714111);ga(''send'', ''event'', ''/bn/jobdetailsBN.asp'', ''click'', ''Print this job'', 4);">&nbsp;প্রিন্ট</a><a href="javascript:void(0);" onclick="ga(''send'', ''event'', ''/bn/jobdetailsBN.asp'', ''click'', '' View all jobs of this company'', 5);">&nbsp;এই কোম্পানির অন্যান্য সব চাকরি</a><a href="javascript:void(0);" onclick="ga(''send'', ''event'', ''/bn/jobdetailsBN.asp'', ''click'', ''Report this job'', 6);">&nbsp;রিপোর্ট</a></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>&nbsp;</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Courses from Bdjobs Training</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Pay online and get 20% discount</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href="http://bdjobstraining.com/trainingdetails.asp?TrainingId=91095&amp;upcoming=0">Export- Import Business Guideline with Commercial, Marketing, Costing &amp; Documentation Procedure</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Classes/ Sessions:</strong>&nbsp;2 Days Long</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Course Duration:</strong>&nbsp;21 - 22 July 2017</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href="http://bdjobstraining.com/trainingdetails.asp?TrainingId=91095&amp;upcoming=0" target="_blank">&nbsp;Click here for detail</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href="javascript:void(0);" onclick="javascript:document.getElementById(''frmJobApplication'').submit()">অনলাইনে আবেদন</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>অথবা</p>\r\n\r\n<p>আপনার জীবনবৃত্তান্ত যেখানে পাঠাবেন&nbsp;<strong>roshni.sanyal@maersk.com</strong>&nbsp;অথবা&nbsp;<strong>মাই বিডিজবসের</strong>&nbsp;মাধ্যমে পাঠাতে&nbsp;<a href="javascript:EmailSend()">এখানে ক্লিক করুন</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>আবেদনকারীকে অবশ্যই জীবনবৃত্তান্তের সাথে&nbsp;ছবি&nbsp;পাঠাতে হবে</p>\r\n\r\n<p>আবেদনের শেষ তারিখ :&nbsp;<strong>জুলাই ২৭, ২০১৭</strong></p>\r\n', '2017-07-13 21:21:22', '2017-07-13 23:31:50', 1, 'Mamun Shahriar', '1', 'bangla', '', 0, 0),
(1500002563, 4, 'Asst. Manager - Store  Palmal Group of Industries', 'featured_images_1500002563.png', '', '', '<p>Asst. Manager - Store</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Palmal Group of Industries<br />\r\nView all jobs of this company<br />\r\nVacancy<br />\r\n02<br />\r\nJob Description / Responsibility<br />\r\nManage and maintain accurate Receive and Issue records of all materials, Inventory taking, Quality checking as per procedure.<br />\r\nEnsure proper maintain and operation of the store like safe receipt, storage, retrieval and timely dispatch.<br />\r\nEnsure goods inbound &amp; out bound, warehouse management, safety and security within the store. Ensure proper deliveries.<br />\r\nMake sure inventory control. Ensure minimum stock level.<br />\r\nMonitor warehouse activities to ensure that goods are stored correctly and safely and warehouse space is used efficiently.<br />\r\nKeep costs and other overheads within the budgeted limit.<br />\r\nDevelop and maintain software based system for materials delivering to the production floor as per plan.<br />\r\nMaintain close liaison with Merchandising Department and cater their requirement successfully.<br />\r\nFollow and implement the operational strategies and procedures according to the company policy.<br />\r\nLead and guide the store personnel to accomplish the assigned/ vested task in best possible way.<br />\r\nEnsure daily/weekly stock report.<br />\r\nJob Nature<br />\r\nFull-time<br />\r\nEducational Requirements<br />\r\nGraduate/ Masters in any discipline<br />\r\nPost graduation diploma/ professional certificates in supply chain management will be treated as additional qualification<br />\r\nExperience Requirements<br />\r\n6 to 8 year(s)<br />\r\nThe applicants should have experience in the following area(s):<br />\r\nStore<br />\r\nThe applicants should have experience in the following business area(s):<br />\r\nGarments<br />\r\nJob Requirements<br />\r\nAge 28 to 35 year(s)<br />\r\nGood knowledge &amp; skills in MS Office package.<br />\r\nStrong technical knowledge in Store system &amp; it&#39;s SOP.<br />\r\nAble to work under pressure and complete the task within a preset time-frame.<br />\r\nAbility to effectively communicate and correspond with the concern department and external suppliers.<br />\r\nMust have the ability to supervise and inspire team members.<br />\r\nJob Location<br />\r\nDhaka Division<br />\r\nSalary Range<br />\r\nNegotiable<br />\r\nOther Benefits<br />\r\nAs Per Company Policy<br />\r\nJob Source<br />\r\nBdjobs.com Online Job Posting<br />\r\nJob Summary<br />\r\nPublished on:&nbsp;Jul 13, 2017</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Vacancy:&nbsp;02</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Job Nature:&nbsp;Full-time</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Experience:&nbsp;6 to 8 year(s)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Age:&nbsp;28 to 35 year(s)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Job Location:&nbsp;Dhaka Division</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Salary Range:&nbsp;Negotiable</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Application Deadline:&nbsp;Aug 12, 2017</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;Shortlist this job<br />\r\n&nbsp;Share by Email<br />\r\n&nbsp;Print this job<br />\r\n&nbsp;View all jobs of this company<br />\r\n&nbsp;Report this job<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp;<br />\r\nCourses from Bdjobs Training<br />\r\nPay online and get 20% discount<br />\r\nHow to Setup (Small Scale) Buying House &amp; Garments<br />\r\nClasses/ Sessions:&nbsp;1 Day</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Course Duration:&nbsp;Friday, July 28, 2017</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Class Schedule:&nbsp;Friday</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;Click here for detail<br />\r\nApply Online</p>\r\n', '2017-07-13 21:22:43', '2017-07-13 23:32:51', 1, 'Mamun Shahriar', '1', 'bangla', '', 0, 0),
(1500002626, 4, 'Deputy Manager (Distribution), BLPGL Mongla Plant  Bashundhara Group', 'featured_images_1500002626.jpeg', '', '', '<p>খালি পদের সংখ্যা</p>\r\n\r\n<p>০১</p>\r\n\r\n<p>চাকরির বিবরণ / দায়িত্বসমূহ</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Supervise day to day distribution process of LP Gas plant which includes Vehicle in, tracking empty cylinders.</li>\r\n	<li>Ensure timely delivery of LP gas through cylinder, tanker etc. all over Bangladesh by using own / hired transport, effectively.</li>\r\n	<li>Ensure plant to plant LPG transfer by road tankers &amp; vessel.</li>\r\n	<li>Ensure delivery data input into SAP Software.</li>\r\n	<li>Ensure and coordinate with line supervisor for distribution support.</li>\r\n	<li>Maintain sales &amp; distribution related documents</li>\r\n	<li>Maintain strong relationship with sales, Production &amp; supply chain department for taking necessary inventory plan.</li>\r\n	<li>Provide guidance &amp; training to all transport officials &amp; logistics department regarding distribution issue.</li>\r\n	<li>Prepare various reports for different stakeholders on a regular basis.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>চাকরির ধরন</p>\r\n\r\n<p>ফুল টাইম</p>\r\n\r\n<p>শিক্ষাগত যোগ্যতা</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Graduate in any discipline.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>অভিজ্ঞতা</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>কমপক্ষে ৬ বছর</li>\r\n	<li>চাকরিপ্রার্থীদের যেসব ক্ষেত্রে অভিজ্ঞতা থাকতে হবেঃ<br />\r\n	Distribution/Supply Chain Management</li>\r\n	<li>চাকরিপ্রার্থীদের যেসব ব্যবসায়িক প্রতিষ্ঠানে অভিজ্ঞতা থাকতে হবেঃ<br />\r\n	LPG Gas/Cylinder Gas</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>অন্যান্য যোগ্যতা</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>বয়স ৩৫ বছর অথবা এর নীচে</li>\r\n	<li>Computer skills in MS Office.</li>\r\n	<li>Knowledge of SAP Software will get preference.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>কর্মস্হল</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Bagerhat (Mongla)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>বেতন সীমা</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>আলোচনা সাপেক্ষ</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>অন্যান্য&nbsp;সুবিধাদি</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Two Festival Bonus, Provident Fund, Gratuity, Subsidized Lunch facility, etc. as per company policy.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>উত্স</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Bdjobs.com Online Job Posting</p>\r\n', '2017-07-13 21:23:46', '2017-07-13 21:23:46', 1, 'Mamun Shahriar', '1', 'bangla', '', 0, 0);
